-- Nikkei 225 Futures Unchanged in Singapore After BOJ
-- B y   A n n a   K i t a n a k a
-- 2013-09-05T02:47:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-05/nikkei-225-futures-unchanged-in-singapore-after-boj.html
Japanese stock futures held declines
after the central bank issued a policy statement.  Nikkei 225 Stock Average futures traded at 14,075 in
 Singapore  as of 11:45 a.m. in Tokyo. Before the Bank of Japan
announcement, the Nikkei 225 gained 0.1 percent to 14,060.52 at
the trading break in Tokyo. The broader Topix index added 0.1
percent to 1,156.99.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anna Kitanaka in Tokyo at 
 akitanaka@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah McDonald at 
 smcdonald23@bloomberg.net  